   <meta content="Cambridge Health Alliance is an academic community health care system committed to serving all members of our communities. We have expertise in primary care, mental health and substance abuse, and caring for diverse and complex populations. CHA patients receive high quality care in convenient neighborhood locations, and have seamless access to advanced care through CHA’s affiliation with Beth Israel Deaconess Medical Center. With over 150,000 patients in Cambridge, Somerville Everett and Boston’s Metro North, CHA is working hard to make sure it can over the integrated services its communities need now, and in the future." name="description"/>
